{"tid":1846870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猜猜港豬何時能做到全港大罷工","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T20:23:11.000Z","uid":254183,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"56ed89fb19cb61cf1620a684a17f1b0948480625","tid":1846870,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"A.1/29<br />\nB.第一例肺炎死亡出現<br />\nC.醫療系統爆煲<br />\nD.香港武漢化<br />\nE.一同落地獄都要返工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cbd6b7b15a676ce7bfe2ea1b7752f27ee8f14a","tid":1846870,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:32:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港醫護、海關唔罷工嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，一齊罷工保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb5fd6b9d811bc153708e7a7d369abc5a88b05e5","tid":1846870,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:36:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a7d4e2afa0c7f1f8e0d0dbadb207508edc8376","tid":1846870,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"爭取真普選時<br />\n港豬唔願意為爭取政治權利全面罷工<br />\n反送中條例時<br />\n香港人也唔願意為爭取自由權利全面罷工<br />\n現在武漢肺炎來了<br />\n已經到了為生存權利而戰的時候<br />\n仲唔全面罷工<br />\n那就一同落地獄搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a8b0798d326cdde999d2f3a780752b1c39fc0c","tid":1846870,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sX9FSQTOy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9sX9FSQTOy8&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5pMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=d9a52514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9sX9FSQTOy8</a><br />\n緊急呼籲！香港人救自己！未來將一日感染20萬人？！〈蕭若元：理論蕭析〉2020-01-28"},{"pid":"5ad7479d4f579b09c004988bd346930753afeb7b","tid":1846870,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:47:49.000Z","msg":"冇人猜咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a766f776579730da5bf12a3c520db4924a9a7e0","tid":1846870,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:48:54.000Z","msg":"估就估啦<br />\n猜咩猜呀大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880fc461e7f6573cfe09c9120f053ab6d74dc6bb","tid":1846870,"uid":254183,"like":0,"d